Final Project

Surya Manavalan
CSCI4229/5229 Fall 2022

Full Chess Game.

Key bindings:
  arrows     Change view angle in overhead
  o/p        Zoom in and out in overhead
  ESC        Exit
  r/R        Restarts game when finished
  Type in commands to move pieces in the format: e2,e4

Running:
  Type in the "make" command to build.
  enter "./final" to run.

